            <scopecontent id="aspace_b60ec982bb2d59ba764812129d80f960">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Carbon copies of three letters: Oughterson to Robert Zollinger, Peter Bent Brigham Hospital, Boston, 1946 February 1;  James P. Cooney, Atomic Energy Commission, to Oughterson, 1950 March 31; George Baehr, Health Insurance Plan of Greater New York, to Oughterson, 1955 June 20.  Oughterson supported prepaid medical insurance plans.</p>
            </scopecontent>
         </c>
         <c id="ref3" level="file">
            <did>
               <unittitle>Notebook on travel to and arrival in Japan</unittitle>
               <unitdate unitdatetype="inclusive">1945</unitdate>
